<div class="inner" id="msg_792187"><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size">目录/Index</span></strong><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">PLAYER SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;2楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 追加数据与新规则<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;3楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 吞食奈落者“英灵级”<br><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;4楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 英灵级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;5楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 战鸟级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;6楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 装甲恐龙<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;7楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 奥迹级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;8楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 金属生命<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;9楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 守护神特技</span><br><span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;10楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：英灵级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;11楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：战鸟级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;12楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：装甲恐龙<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;13楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：奥迹级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;14楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：金属生命<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;15楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：泛用守护神（米勒斯）&amp;泛用武装</span><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">WORLD SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;16楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 魔法王国雷姆利亚<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;17楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 恐龙王国希柏里尔<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;18楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 机械生命体金属生命<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;19楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 秘密结社特拉尼西亚<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;20楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 国家与组织<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;21楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 人物列表<br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">GAMEMASTER SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;22楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy资料的作成<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;23楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy特技<br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;24楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy：守护神<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;25楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy：人类之敌<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;26楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy：其他Enemy</span><br></div>
