</h4>
<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_835087_extra_info">
<li class="title">働きたくない<li class="membergroup">版主<li class="stars"><img src="Themes/celeste/images/off.png" alt="*" border="0"/><li class="avatar" style="overflow: auto;">
